---
title: "Story Understanding in Video Advertisements"
collection: publications
permalink: /publication/2018-story
date: 2018-09-02
venue: 'British Machine Vision Conference (BMVC)'
paperurl: 'https://arxiv.org/abs/1807.11122'
---


We make progress in how to understand the dynamic structure of video advertisements. In particular, we present approaches to effectively predict climax and sentiment in ads.

